Package: ferols
Type: Package
Title: Fixed-Effects Robust OLS via IRWLS (Huber M)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Joachim", "Gassen", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
    email = "gassen@wiwi.hu-berlin.de",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4364-2911"))
Description: Experimental tools for estimating fixed-effects linear models using 
  Huber M-estimation via iteratively reweighted least squares (IRWLS). The package
  builds on the 'fixest' framework to absorb high-dimensional fixed effects and
  provides robust sandwich variance estimators with fixest-style interfaces.
  This is early-stage, work-in-progress research software; the API and numerical
  behavior may change and the package should not yet be used for reproducible 
  empirical analysis.
